\ip \bd ?Pah t…ôm…ôte naoa u?\bd* Jon Mak t…ôm…ôte naoa u. In s…ôn…ôm…ô et…ôm tuelef kit r…ôha Iesu. M…ôto kat…ôn m…ôm…ô in fren w…®r kit r…ôha Pita it…ôm ilau katian ik…®n m…®n tep…ôt. Naoa r…ôha W…ôk M…®n tat…ôn m…ôm…ô in t…ômuw…®n ilau Pol e r…ôhan naliw…ôk…ôn t…ômaup…ôn mol, k…ôn uaris…®g lan, t…ômuw…®n ilau Panapas.  
\ip \bd ?T…ôm…ôte tatuw…®n k…ôm pah?\bd* K…ômot…ôn m…ôm…ô Mak t…ôm…ôtat…®g Rom nian in t…ôm…ôte naoa u, k…ôn ok…ôm-naka in ilau Pita, uaris…®g kohamnu Pita. Mak t…ôm…ôte naoa u tuw…®n o i…ôfak m…®n …ôp…ôh Rom u ilat Iaihlu…ô m…®n. Kitat kot…®tun n…ôhlan m…ôto-inu in tat…ôn-iar…ôp n…®p…ôt…® nol…ôn m…®n r…ôha net…ôm Isrel it…ôm koatol. K…ôn e naoa u, t…ôm…ôte n…ôghat…ôn neen e n…ôghat…ôn Arameik it…ôm net…ôm Isrel k…®not…®tun r…ôk…®s. M…ôto in m…ôuhlin n…ôghat…ôn m…®n u tuwa e n…ôghat…ôn Kris it…ôm Iaihlu…ô m…®n …ôp…ôh Rom koat…ôghat lan.  
\ip \bd ?N…ômeg…ôh…ôn tahro nulan nian t…ôm…ôte?\bd* E nian Mak t…ôm…ôte naoa u, k…ôn net…ôm Rom koat…ôr…ôm…ôr…ô e n…®t…ôn asol it…ôm t…®t…ôlau-in N…®t…ôh…ôi Metiterenian. R…ôhalat n…ôghat…ôn kiti…ôh …ôm, k…ôn r…ôhalat suat…®p kot…ôw…®r, k…ôn r…ôhalat nol…ôn o nahl-ip…ôn…ôn n…ôghat…ôn m…®n in t…ôw…®r. Nian …ôh, in nian t…ôw…®r o n…ôn-iar…ôp…ôn Namnus…ôn T…ôw…®r r…ôha Iesu Kristo. E nian …ôh, Namnus…ôn T…ôw…®r t…ômaiu u…ôhai …ôm e n…®t…ôn p…®s…®n p…®s…®n m…®n e suat…®p m…®n r…ôha Rom.  
\ip \bd ?T…ôm…ôte naoa u o naka?\bd* Mak tolkeike m…ôm…ô ot…ôn-iar…ôp …ôtuat…®p namnus…ôn rafin r…ôha Iesu, m…ôm…ô in pah, k…ôn in t…ômol naka, k…ôn mat…ôg…ôtun naka. Ok…ôm-naka in tolkeike m…ôm…ô ot…®l…ôs-ip…ôr n…ôt…ôl…®g…ôn r…ôha i…ôfak m…®n …ôp…ôh Rom, m…ôto-inu net…ômim tep…ôt k…ômotol n…ôrat…ôn elat. Mak t…ôm…ôte tep…ôt e nian i…ôk…®s m…®n it…ôm ot…ôpanuwa e n…ômeg…ôh…ôn r…ôha net…ômim r…ôha Iesu. K…ôn in t…ôm…ôn-iar…ôp nol…ôn r…ôha Iesu m…ôm…ô in m…®n t…ôm…ôtat…®g e nian i…ôk…®s m…®n.  
\c 1  
\s1 Jon Baptais t…ômol …ôpen-…ôpen…ô e suat…®p  
