\v 3 ‚ÄúSuah kit t…ôtaun …ôp…ôh ik…®n taru…ôn-aru…ôn ik…®n mat…ôn m…ôm…ô, ‚ÄòIt…ômat, otol …ôpen-…ôpen…ô o suat…®p r…ôha I…ôr…ôm…ôr…ô, k…ôn motol r…ôhan suat…®p t…ôtuat…®p.‚Äô‚Äù\x - \xo 1:3 \xt Aes 40:3\x*   
\p
\v 4 K…ôn tol n…ôhlan, Jon Baptais t…ômiet-pa ik…®n taru…ôn-aru…ôn ik…®n matol baptais e net…ômim, k…ôn mat…ôn-iar…ôp n…ôghat…ôn r…ôha Uhg…®n k…ôm ilat m…ôm…ô okot…ôk…ôike mot…ôuhlin m…ôntaalat o nol…ôn rat m…®n r…ôhalat, k…ôn motuw…®n o Uhg…®n, m…ôm…ô in otaf…ôl nol…ôn rat m…®n r…ôhalat. K…ôn e n…ômt…ôtin kit, okol baptais elat.\x - \xo 1:4 \xt W…ôk 13:24; 19:4 \x*  
\v 5 Net…ômim rafin r…ôha n…®t…ôn …ôh Jutia ne taon …ôh Jerusalem, k…ômotuwa mot…ôt…ôl…®g-in r…ôhan n…ôghat…ôn k…ôn mot…ôn-iar…ôp r…ôhalat nol…ôn rat m…®n, k…ôn Jon t…ômol baptais elat …ôp…ôh e n…ôhau Jotan.   
\p
\v 6 Jon t…ôm…ôsuw…®n…ôn e nat…®mnat w…®r. R…ôhan nat…®mnat tahmen …ôm e r…ôha ien u Elaija aup…ôn. R…ôhan nat…®mnat k…ômol e n…®m…ôme kamel, k…ôn r…ôhn k…ôt…ôut k…ômol e nuwig…® kau, k…ôn matun …ôm pit…®p ne nahui sukapak e n…®kinat.\x - \xo 1:6 \xt 2 King 1:8; Mat 11:8 \x*  
\v 7 K…ôn t…ômat…ôn-iar…ôp k…ôm net…ômim m…ôm…ô, ‚ÄúSuah kit u tatuaris…®g-in io, r…ôhan n…ôsan…ôn…ôn ne nep…ôt…ôn tapr…ôk…®s-in io. Io ek…ôsahmen-in m…®n…ôn m…ôm…ô ekeiuaiu mapeg r…ôk…®s r…ôhan put.\x - \xo 1:7 \xt W…ôk 13:25 \x*  
\v 8 Ekatol baptais et…ômat e n…ôhau, m…ôto in ot…ôpanol baptais et…ômat e Narm…®n R…ôha Uhg…®n.‚Äù   
