\v 10 Nian Iesu t…ôm…ôr …ôp…ôh e n…ôhau, k…ôn mas…®p…ôr m…ôplan nego e neai t…ômer…ôh, k…ôn Narm…®n R…ôha Uhg…®n t…ômeiuaiu-pa ron tahmen-p…ôn e mak.  
\v 11 K…ôn n…ôghat…ôn kit t…ôm…®s…®-p…ôr …ôp…ôh e nego e neai mat…ôn min-nulan m…ôm…ô, ‚ÄúIk net…®k keike, ekolkeike p…®k ik, k…ôn n…®kik tagien p…®k ag…®n ron ik.‚Äù\x - \xo 1:11 \xt Sam 2:7; Aes 42:1; Mat 12:18; Mak 9:7 \x*   
\s1 Setan t…ômos-ip…ôn-os-ip…ôn  //  k…ôm Iesu  
\r (Mat 4:1-11; Luk 4:1-13)  
\p
\v 12 K…ôn roiu ag…®n-…ôh m…®n, Narm…®n R…ôha Uhg…®n t…ômit-ip…ôn Iesu …ôp…ôh ik…®n taru…ôn-aru…ôn ik…®n,  
\v 13 ima nat iarup…®n m…®n. T…ômat…®g ik…®n mos nian fote. Nian m…®n Setan tatos-ip…ôn-os-ip…ôn k…ôm in. K…ôn nagelo m…®n k…ômotasitu lan.\x - \xo 1:13 \xt Sam 91:11-13 \x*   
\s1 Iesu t…®nat…ôtuoun mat…ôn-iar…ôp Namnus…ôn T…ôw…®r  
