\p
\v 14 Nian k…®n…®l…ôs-ip…ôn r…ôk…®s Jon e kalapus, Iesu t…ômuw…®n …ôp…ôh Kalili mat…ôn-iar…ôp Namnus…ôn T…ôw…®r r…ôha Uhg…®n k…ôm net…ômim.\x - \xo 1:14 \xt Mak 6:17 \x*  
\v 15 T…ôm…ôn m…ôm…ô, ‚Äú!Ure! !R…ôhan nian t…®nuwa! !Nian r…ôha n…ôr…ôm…ôr…ô…ôn r…ôha Uhg…®n t…®natuwa iu…ôhk…®r! !Ot…ôuhlin n…ôt…ôl…®g…ôn r…ôhat…ômat, motap…ôs pahrien nol…ôn rat m…®n, k…ôn motuw…®n o Uhg…®n, k…ôn motahat…ôt…ô e Namnus…ôn T…ôw…®r!‚Äù\x - \xo 1:15 \xt Mat 3:2 \x*   
