\p
\v 16 Nian Iesu t…ôm…ôtaliw…ôk e n…®kal…® Lek Kalili, k…ôn m…ôplan suah mil k…ôiu, et…ômim r…ôha niuw…ôn n…ôm m…®n, n…ôrg…®lau u Saimon ne pian Antru. K…ôtuat…®p-in r…ôhalau net.  
