\v 20 K…ôn e nian …ôm …ôh in…ôh, Iesu t…ômaun-in ilau lan, k…ôn ku…ôtul muap…ôs r…ôhalau tata Sepeti ne r…ôhan iolw…ôk m…®n kot…ôp…ôl…ôh e n…®p…ôg noa pot, k…ôn mu…ôt…ôu-p…ôn Iesu.   
