\p
\v 38 M…ôto Iesu t…ôm…ôn-ip…ôn k…ôm ilat m…ôm…ô, ‚ÄúK…ôp…ô. P…ôs kotuw…®n …ôp…ôh e latu…ônu p…®s…®n m…®n neen, ekamnus-iar…ôp r…ôhak n…ôghat…ôn k…ôm net…ômim map…ôkol m…ôto-inu, nat …ôh in …ôh emuwa ron m…ôm…ô ekol.‚Äù   
\p
\v 39 K…ôn muw…®n map…ôkol rafin e n…®t…ôn …ôp…ôh Kalili, m…ôtamnus-iar…ôp r…ôhan n…ôghat…ôn …ôp…ôh e nim…ô r…ôha nu…ôf…®m…®n…ôn m…®n, k…ôn m…ôhg-iar…ôp narm…®n rat m…®n e net…ômim.\x - \xo 1:39 \xt Mat 4:23; 9:35 \x*   
\s1 Iesu t…ômol-w…®r suah kit leprosi t…ômol  
\r (Mat 8:1-4; Luk 5:12-16)  
\p
\v 40 Suah kit leprosi t…ômol t…ômuwa m…®sin-p…ôn nul…®n o Iesu m…ôtas…ôkin-p…ôn n…ôw…®r…ôn ron m…ôm…ô, ‚ÄúOk…ôm…ô nakolkeike, k…ôn n…ôk…®tun nol-w…®r…ôn io k…ôn maf…ôl r…ôk…®s namk…®m…®k…ôn lak.‚Äù   
\p
