\m
\v 1 Nian neen k…®notuwa r…ôk…®s m…®notuw…®n, Iesu t…ôm…®t…ôl…®g-p…ôn m…®n …ôp…ôh Kapaneam, k…ôn n…ôghat…ôn t…ômaiu muw…®n k…ôm net…ômim m…®n m…ôm…ô Iesu …ôp…ôh r…ôhan nim…ô.\fig |alt="paralyzed man lowered through roof to Jesus" src="LB00305B.TIF" size="col" loc="Mrk 2:1-7" ref="Mak 2:1" \fig*  
\v 2 K…ôn net…ômim tep…ôt k…ômotuwa mot…ôr w…®r …ôp…ôh im…ô, ne ihlu…ô ne, k…ôn rum t…®k…ô o et…ômim kit m…®n. K…ôn Iesu tat…ôn-iar…ôp r…ôhan n…ôghat…ôn k…ôm ilat.   
\p
\v 3 K…ôn suah kuw…®t k…ômotalis pialat kit motuwa o Iesu it…ôm n…®p…ôt…®n m…ôs…®n t…ôm…®m…®s m…ôtap…®l-p…ôr e r…ôhan n…®m…®tiw…®n.  
\v 4 Nian k…ômotuwa, m…ôto net…ômim k…®not…ôr …ôp…ôh im…ô, k…ôn okol kot…ôruru nuw…®n…ôn kehm Iesu. K…ôn kot…®l…ôs motuw…®n …ôp…ôh il…®s e nim…ô motos-ir…ôk…®s n…ôhg…® nim…ô m…ôs…®n …ôtuat…®p …ôm …ôh Iesu tat…ôtul ik…®n im…ô,\f + \fr 2:4 \ft E nian …ôh, k…ômol n…ôhg…® nim…ô neen e tael. K…ôn net…ôm m…®n u k…ômotos-ir…ôk…®s tael m…®n neen m…ôm…ô otol kuhal tahmen-in suah u it…ôm in tat…®m…®s.\f* k…ôn mot…ôhlman-…ôhlman suah un tatite e n…®m…®tiw…®n r…ôhan muw…®n iu…ôhk…®r …ôm o Iesu.  
