\p
\v 6 M…ôto i…ôg…ôtun m…®n neen r…ôha Lou kot…ôp…ôl…ôh …ôp…ôh im…ô, k…ôn n…®kilat t…ôm…ôht m…ôm…ô,  
\v 7 ‚Äú?Tahro suah u tat…ôn rat Uhg…®n? N…ôghat…ôn …ôh t…ôrat. Uhg…®n …ôm t…®tun nos-ir…ôk…®s…ôn nol…ôn rat r…ôha et…ômim. !Pah m…®n t…®tun nos-ir…ôk…®s…ôn!‚Äù   
