\v 15 K…ôn nian kit, Iesu t…ômuw…®n m…ôtagw…ôn …ôp…ôh ima Lifae ik…®n ilat net…ômim r…ôha nos…ôn m…ôni r…ôha tak…®s, ne net…ôm nol t…ôfag…ô rat neen. Kotagw…ôn …ôm kiti…ôh ilat Iesu ne r…ôhan m…®n net…ômim m…ôto-inu net…ômim tep…ôt kotol t…ôfag…ô rat n…ôhlan kotuaris…®g-in Iesu.  
\v 16 I…ôg…ôtun r…ôha Lou neen, ilat u Farisi. K…ôn neen k…ômot…ôplan m…ôm…ô Iesu t…ôtagw…ôn …ôm kiti…ôh ilat nol t…ôfag…ô m…®n un, ne net…ômim r…ôha nos…ôn m…ôni r…ôha tak…®s, k…ôn kot…ôtap…ôh o net…ômim r…ôhan m…®n m…ôm…ô, ‚Äú?Tahro Iesu t…ôtagw…ôn …ôm kiti…ôh ilat net…ôm koatol n…ôhlan?‚Äù\x - \xo 2:16 \xt Mat 11:19 \x*   
