\v 25-26 Iesu t…ômuhalp…®n r…ôhalat n…ôghat…ôn m…ôm…ô, ‚ÄúOk…ôm-naka it…ômat nak…ôsotafin…ôn …ôh nat u Tef…®t t…ômol aup…ôn nian Apiata in pris asol ag…®n r…ôha Uhg…®n. It…ômat n…®notafin r…ôk…®s m…ôm…ô Tef…®t n…ôum…®s t…ômus, k…ôn tuw…®n …ôp…ôh e Nim…ô Tapol…ôn r…ôha Uhg…®n, k…ôn m…®l…ôs p…®ret asim u pris m…®n …ôm koatun, k…ôn in m…®l…ôs muwa motun ilat in m…®n neen.‚Äù\x - \xo 2:25-26 \xt 1 Saml 21:1-6 \x*\x - \xo 2:25-26 \xt Lev 24:5-9 \x*   
