\p
\v 38 K…ôn Iesu t…ôm…ôn-ip…ôn k…ôm ilau m…ôm…ô, ‚ÄúIt…ômlau n…ôku…ôruru nat u nakatu…ôn. ?Tahro? ?It…ômlau, n…®kit…ôlau t…ôht m…ôm…ô n…ôkuahmen m…ôm…ô kit…ôhal k…ôhal…ôtul e n…®g…ôm r…ôha nuwig…® nien it…ôm io ek…ôike m…ôtul lan?\f + \fr 10:38 \ft N…ôghat…ôn Kris …ôtuat…®p tat…ôn m…ôm…ô, ‚Äú?It…ômlau, n…®kit…ôlau t…ôht m…ôm…ô n…ôkuahmen m…ôm…ô kit…ôhal ok…ôhal…ôn…®m k…ôl…ôh e kap r…ôha n…ôto…ôn nahm…ô…ôn it…ôm io ek…ôike m…ôn…®m lan?‚Äù\f* ?K…ôn muahmen-in m…®n m…ôm…ô okol baptais et…ômlau e nahm…ô…ôn m…ôm…ô okol mihin lak?‚Äù\x - \xo 10:38 \xt Mak 14:36; Luk 12:50 \x*   
\p
\v 39 K…ôn ku…ôm…ô, ‚Äú!∆èw…ôh, ekuahmen in!‚Äù M…ôto Iesu t…ôm…ô, ‚ÄúPahrien, onaku…ôk…ôike mu…ôtul e n…®g…ôm r…ôha nuwig…® nien it…ôm io ek…ôike m…ôtul lan. K…ôn okol baptais et…ômlau e baptais it…ôm okol baptais lak lan.\x - \xo 10:39 \xt W…ôk 12:2; Nol ∆èp…ôn 1:9 \x*  
\v 40 M…ôto o n…ôp…ôl…ôh…ôn e n…®kal…®k mat…®p ne mol, s…ôn…ôm…ô r…ôhak m…ôm…ô ek…ôn. Ik…®n mil …ôh, ilau r…ôha net…ôm m…®n u it…ôm Uhg…®n t…ômol …ôpen-…ôpen…ô olat.‚Äù   
\s1 Et…ôm t…ôm…ô otep…ôt e net…ômim  
\r (Mat 20:24-28)  
\p
\v 41 Nian r…ôhan net…ôm ten k…ômot…ôto n…ôghat…ôn un, k…ôn nem…ôha t…ômol ilat o Jemes ne Jon.  
\v 42 K…ôn Iesu t…ômaun-in r…ôhan m…®n net…ômim kotuwa, k…ôn t…ôn-ip…ôn k…ôm ilat m…ôm…ô, ‚ÄúIt…ômat n…ôkot…®tun m…ôm…ô net…ôm m…®n u kot…ôm…ô okotep…ôt e Iaihlu…ô m…®n, kotos-ip…ôr at…®p ilat, k…ôn net…ôm-iasol r…ôhalat koatal…®kiamt…ô r…ôhalat m…®n net…ômim.\x - \xo 10:42 \xt Luk 22:25-26 \x*   
\p
\v 43 ‚ÄúM…ôto it…ômat on…ôk…ôsotol…ôn min-n…ôhlan. Ok…ôm…ô it…ômat kit tolkeike m…ôm…ô in otep…ôt et…ômat, in ot…ôk…ôike muwa m…ôm…ô in iolw…ôk …ôm kit r…ôhat…ômat.\x - \xo 10:43 \xt Mat 23:11; Mak 9:35 \x*  
\v 44 K…ôn ok…ôm…ô it…ômat kit tolkeike m…ôm…ô in otit it…ômat, k…ôn in ot…ôk…ôike muwa m…ôm…ô in slef kit r…ôhat…ômat.  
\v 45 K…ôn io m…®n, Net…® Et…ômim, em…ôsuwam…ôn m…ôm…ô net…ômim okotol w…ôk k…ôm io, m…ôto emuwa m…ôm…ô ekol w…ôk k…ôm net…ômim k…ôn mos-ip…ôn r…ôhak n…ômeg…ôh…ôn m…ôm…ô ek…®k…®s ilat e r…ôhalat nol…ôn rat m…®n.‚Äù   
\s1 Iesu t…ômol-w…®r n…®gan…ômt…® Patimias  
\r (Mat 20:29-34; Luk 18:35-43)  
\p
\v 46 K…ôn Iesu ne r…ôhan m…®n net…ômim, k…ômotuwa …ôp…ôh Jeriko. K…ôn nian k…®notiet moatuw…®n, k…ôn net…ômim tep…ôt k…ômotuaris…®g-in ilat. K…ôn suah kit n…®gan…ômt…®n t…ôp…®s, tat…ôp…ôl…ôh e n…®kal…® suat…®p, n…ôrg…®n u Patimeas net…® Timeas. Nian rafin tat…ôtap…ôh-in m…ôni o net…ômim.  
\v 47 Nian t…ôm…ôto m…ôm…ô Iesu et…ôm Nasaret t…ôtaliw…ôk e suat…®p matuwa, k…ôn t…ômag…ôt …ôf…ôm…ôh m…ôm…ô, ‚Äú!Awi, Iesu Mip…® Tef…®t, as…ôkitun io, masitu lak!‚Äù   
\p
\v 48 K…ôn net…ômim neen kot…ôm…ôr…®t lan mot…ôm…ô, ‚Äú!Ei, …ôsag…ôt…ôn!‚Äù mot…ôn pap m…ôto in t…ôm…ôha mag…ôt …ôf…ôm…ôh p…®k m…®n m…ôm…ô, ‚Äú!Mip…® Tef…®t, as…ôkitun io, masitu lak!‚Äù   
\p
\v 49 K…ôn Iesu t…ôtul k…ôn m…ôn m…ôm…ô, ‚ÄúOtaun-in-p…ôn-tu suah un m…ôm…ô tuwa.‚Äù K…ôn mot…ôn-ip…ôn k…ôm in m…ôm…ô, ‚ÄúEi, agien, m…ôtul, m…ôto-inu Iesu t…ôtaun-in ik.‚Äù   
\p
\v 50 K…ôn suah un t…ômat…®pin r…ôhn kot, m…ôt…®p m…ôr muw…®n o Iesu.  
\v 51 K…ôn Iesu t…ôm…ôtap…ôh ron m…ôm…ô, ‚Äú?Nakolkeike naka?‚Äù M…ôto t…ôm…ô, ‚ÄúI…ôg…ôtun, ekolkeike m…ôm…ô nakol-w…®r n…®gan…ômt…ôk p…ôs ekehm nat.‚Äù   
\p
\v 52 K…ôn Iesu t…ôm…ô, ‚ÄúAtuw…®n. R…ôham nahat…ôt…ô…ôn t…®nol-w…®r ik.‚Äù K…ôn roiu ag…®n m…®n n…®gan…ômt…®n t…ôm…ôw…®r, t…®natehm nat. K…ôn m…®nat…ôt…ôu-p…ôn Iesu moatan.\x - \xo 10:52 \xt Mak 5:34 \x*   
\c 11  
\s1 Iesu t…ômasu…ô e togki  //  matuw…®n Jerusalem  
\r (Mat 21:1-11; Luk 19:28-40;  //  Jon 12:12-19)  
\m
\v 1 K…ômotuw…®n iu…ôhk…®r o Jerusalem, iu…ôhk…®r o latu…ônu mil un Petfas ne Petani, moatuw…®n …ôp…ôh e N…®tot R…ôha N…®g U Olif, k…ôn Iesu t…ômahl-ip…ôn r…ôhan k…ôiu et…ômim mil kuaup…ôn.  
\v 2 T…ôm…ôn-ip…ôn n…ôghat…ôn u k…ôm ilau m…ôm…ô, ‚ÄúOnakian …ôp…ôh e latu…ônu …ôh kotas…®p…ônin. O nian nakian …ôh-ik…®n, roiu ag…®n onaku…ôplan n…ôt…® togki kit k…ôsasu…ô…ôn …ôh lan k…ôm…ôru…ôtain. K…ôn n…ôkiak…®s muas…®g mueia.  
\v 3 K…ôn ok…ôm…ô suah kit t…ôm…ô, ‚Äò?Onakuahro-in net…® togki?‚Äô k…ôn naku…ôm…ô, ‚ÄòI…ôr…ôm…ôr…ô tolkeike, k…ôn ot…ôpanahl-ipa m…®n ot…ôsuw…ôh…ôn.‚Äô‚Äù   
\p
\v 4 Ilau k…ômian k…ôn mu…ôplan net…® togki un k…ôm…ôru…ôtain e n…®kal suat…®p …ôp…ôh iu…ôhk…®r o nafilu…ô e nim…ô, k…ôn kiak…®s.  
\v 5 M…ôto net…ômim neen k…ômot…ôtul …ôh-ik…®n k…ôn mot…ôtap…ôh olau m…ôm…ô, ‚Äú!Ei! ?Nak…ôtiak…®s net…® togki un o naka?‚Äù   
\p
